======================================================================
                               CFJ 913

"The Bank can have a negative number of a currency."

======================================================================

Judge:       Andre

Judgement:   TRUE

Eligible:    Andre, Antimatter, Blob, Chuck, Crito, elJefe, favor,
             General Chaos, KoJen, Macross, Michael, Morendil, Murphy,
             Steve, Swann, Vanyel, Zefram

Not eligible:
Caller:      Harlequin
